Sun Jun  8 23:43:42 PDT 2003

You can access the Debian menu hierarchy by running

    /etc/X11/ratmenu/debian.menu

Alternatively, you can

    cp /etc/menu-methods/ratmenu $HOME/.menu-methods/

And then run

    update-menus

This will create the dir $HOME/.ratmenu/ with the ratmenu scripts,
with $HOME/.ratmenu/debian.menu as the root menu.

Thanks to Fabricio Matheus Goncalves for this capability in ratmenu.
